hole_5.original_tactic:
cases h₁ with
| inl h₁ => norm_num [h₁]
| inr h₁ =>
  have h₂ : n % 4 = 2 := by simpa [Nat.ModEq, Nat.ModEq] using h₁
  have h₃ : 0 < n := by
    by_contra h₄
    have h₅ : n = 0 := by omega
    rw [h₅] at h₂
    norm_num at h₂
  exact h₃
